### 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 User 1 Signup
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "User1",
  "email": "u1@test.com",
  "password": "pass123"
}

### 🧑‍💻 User 1 Login
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "u1@test.com",
  "password": "pass123"
}

### 🔑 Copy token from above response as TOKEN1, and user._id as USER1_ID


